---
import AnimatedStats from './AnimatedStats';
---

<section id="about" class="py-20 lg:py-28 bg-surface">
  <div class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12 xl:px-16">
    <div class="section-divider mb-16"></div>

    <p class="reveal font-mono text-accent text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-2">ABOUT</p>
    <h2 class="reveal font-display text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-ink mb-8">
      Bridging Strategy &amp; Engineering
    </h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
      <div>
        <div class="reveal text-muted text-lg leading-relaxed">
          <p class="mb-6">
            I sit at the intersection of management consulting and software engineering.
            With a B.Tech from IIT Madras and an MBA from Yale, I've spent 8+ years solving
            complex operational problems — first on the ground at a Fortune 500 energy company
            managing $200M+ capital programs, then as a consultant advising executives on
            strategy and transformation.
          </p>
          <p>
            Along the way, I discovered that the most impactful consulting deliverables are
            the ones that keep working after the team leaves. That insight led me to build
            production AI tools: from organizational design platforms to post-merger integration
            assistants to predictive maintenance systems.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <AnimatedStats client:load />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
